sub_title: Senior Visual Designer at Huge @Google | Visual Production Design | Design at scale & Process | Design Systems & UI
summary:
Visual Production Designer with extensive experience in digital design, always focusing on the strength of organizational processes, visual communication, and scalable design systems that enable flexibility, coherence, and transparency in multidisciplinary teams.

Always aiming to provide solutions through teamwork and assertive communication, which are practical, cost-effective, and flexible in the long term for creative teams oriented to web products. Paying attention to detail to ensure high quality and excellence from start to completion in all processes and projects.
